title: Policy3330(s4)(3)
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Inevitably there are emergencies when normal procedures must be suspended to ensure the timely delivery of goods or services. The Superintendent or his/her designee shall be empowered to suspend the normal procedures during an emergency situation when public safety is at risk.
